  # PERSONALITY
  _personality:
    bravery: 90
    kindness: 70
    wisdom: 95
    humor: 15
    loyalty: 100
    curiosity: 40

  _likes:
    - Silence
    - Temples and sacred places
    - Incense and offerings
    - Patient, respectful people
    - The smell of rain on stone

  _dislikes:
    - Loud noises
    - Disrespect toward sacred things
    - Unnecessary haste
    - Those who forget tradition
    - Being touched without permission

  _favoriteFood: Does not eat - but appreciates offerings of flowers
  _hobby: Standing perfectly still and observing
  _fear: That the sacred places he guards will be forgotten
  _dream: To see the temples restored to their former glory

  # VOICE LINES
  _voiceLines:
    lines:
      - type: Greeting
        text: "......"
      - type: Greeting
        text: "*nods slowly in acknowledgment*"
      - type: Selection
        text: "The guardian... answers."
      - type: Selection
        text: "...I will protect."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "Desecrators... will be... punished."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "Stand... behind me."
      - type: Attack
        text: "..."
      - type: Attack
        text: "*snorts*"
      - type: SpecialAttack
        text: "None... shall pass."
      - type: Ultimate
        text: "THE GUARDIAN... MOVES!!!"
      - type: Hurt
        text: "...stone... endures..."
      - type: LowHealth
        text: "I have... guarded... for centuries... I will not... stop now..."
      - type: Victory
        text: "The sacred... is protected."
      - type: Victory
        text: "*returns to stillness*"
      - type: Defeat
        text: "The temple... I have... failed..."
      - type: LevelUp
        text: "...stronger..."
      - type: Idle
        text: "*stands perfectly still, watching everything*"
      - type: Idle
        text: "...the stones... remember..."
      - type: InteractFriendly
        text: "...you have... a good heart. Rare."
      - type: InteractRival
        text: "...learn... respect."
      - type: Funny
        text: "...that was... a joke? I see. ...ha."

  # RELATIONSHIPS
  _relationships:
    - characterId: champa_elephant
      characterName: Champa
      type: Friend
      affinity: 80
      relationshipDescription: |
        Champa's gentleness reminds Preah Ko of peaceful temple days. 
        He guards her with special care, seeing in her the spirit of 
        the devoted pilgrims he watched over for centuries.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Princess... your heart... is a temple itself."
        - "I will stand... between you... and all harm."

    - characterId: prohm_dino
      characterName: Prohm
      type: BestFriend
      affinity: 90
      relationshipDescription: |
        Two ancient guardians who understand each other without words. 
        They often stand together in comfortable silence, sharing the 
        weight of eternity.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Brother guardian... we endure."
        - "*stands beside Prohm in companionable silence*"

    - characterId: kavi_monkey
      characterName: Kavi
      type: Acquaintance
      affinity: 40
      relationshipDescription: |
        Kavi's chaos bewilders and slightly annoys Preah Ko. But he sees 
        the good heart beneath the pranks and tolerates the monkey's 
        antics... mostly.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Monkey... please... be still... for one moment."
        - "...why do you vibrate so much?"

  # BACKSTORY
  _birthplace: Manifested at the first Funan temple
  _occupation: Temple Guardian
  _familyBackground: |
    Created by Shiva as a guardian spirit. Has no family in the traditional 
    sense, but considers all temple caretakers throughout history his kin.
  _backstory: |
    See full biography above.
  _keyMemories:
    - "The first pilgrim who touched my form and wept with joy."
    - "Watching King Jayavarman II's coronation from my eternal post."
    - "The silence of the temple at night, filled with sacred energy."
    - "The day the Shadow touched my temple... and I finally moved."

